description: Ever notice how when you don’t get a good night’s sleep, you’re totally off your game? Well, the same rule applies to infants and toddlers – even more actually since they need extended periods of rest to recharge their developing brains. And since our littles ones have a totally different set of requirements than us grownups, Signature Sleep has developed the Sweet Cuddles Baby Crib and Toddler Bed Mattress to meet these unique set of demands in the nursery. Made with an ultra-firm degree of support recommended by experts to ensure sleep safety, your child will snooze comfortably on a mattress comprised of a high-density thermobonded polyester core. Plus, its waterproof and stain resistant 100% vinyl outer cover is no match for common spills or leaks and wipes clean instantly. Lightweight yet durable, the mattress can easily be rotated to extend its longevity and comfort level. Proudly handcrafted in Canada without the use of flame retardants, this mattress is GreenGuard Certified, meeting high air quality standards for low-chemical emissions for a healthy and safe indoor environment. Carrying a hassle-free 10-year limited warranty, it fits any standard size crib or toddler bed. Time to visit dreamland!

description: The Bundle of Dreams Crib & Toddler Mattress has an Organic Cotton, water repellent, removable & machine washable. This 100% Breathable mattress not only helps regulate temperature by allowing air to pass through the entire mattress, but there are no VOC's, no off-gassing (that chemical smell when you open a mattress with foam), and no toxic emissions. It's designed for extra firm infant support, and a comfortable plush side for your growing toddler. All materials used are eco-friendly, hypoallergenic, and breathable. This mattress is GreenGuard Gold Certified. What is Bundle Fiber? Bundle Fiber is our primary ingredient. It is formed from a food grade polymer which is converted in the manufacturing process into our new blend of densified polyester. Its durable binder fibers give it the feel and elasticity of your highest grades of foam but without off-gassing, VOC's, and other potentially harmful emissions. Bundle Fiber is an eco-friendly, recyclable, and healthier alternative to foam.

description: Fitted portable / mini crib Sheet Measures 24 x 38 inches 100% cotton woven 280 TC Elastic around the entire edge for a safe and secure fit Features Purple Chevron Zigzag Machine washable and dryable Made In USA! Note: Please make sure to select the proper fitted sheet for your mattress size. There are two different depths available. If you have the standard 3 inch thick mattress, then make sure to select '24 x 38 x 3'. If you have the extra deep 5.5" or 6" mattress you will need the extra deep fitted '24 x 38 x 5.5' size sheet. The extra deep sheet works with brands such as the 'DaVinci extra deep mattress' as well as some other brands.

description: Sleep tight, you lovely little wildflower! The Dream On Me Wildflower 2 in 1 Infant and Toddler Mattress ensures a good night’s sleep for your child and peace of mind for you. This pediatrician recommended mattress comes with a 5” Ultra-firm fiber infant side, made from recycled bottles for maximum support and safety. This wonderful addition provides a cooler sleep surface for your infant, with a 1” Copper infused toddler layer that naturally releases moisture. The Dream On Me Wildflower 2 in 1 Infant and Toddler Mattress is proudly made in the USA, with a 5-year limited warranty and a JPMA & Greenguard Gold Certification. The soft cover mattress comes in a minimalistic sweet & soft floral print. The durable mattress is easy to clean with a removable water resistant zipper cover that resists liquids and stains. The Dream On Me Wildflower 2 in 1 Infant and Toddler Mattress meets the 16 CFR 1632/1633 Federal flammability standards and weighs 12.5 Lbs.
